yoast_head_json.title: Camshaft says Byju's unit beneficial owner of $533 million funds | TechCrunch
yoast_head_json.description: Camshaft disclosed in court filings this week that some $533 million it managed for Byju's Alpha, a U.S. unit of Indian edtech group Byju's, was Camshaft revealed in court filings this week that some $533 million it managed for Byju's Alpha was transferred to another 100% and U.S.-based subsidiary of Byju's.
